quote: If you only knew the power of the dark side!
I find your lack of faith disturbing.
You have failed me for the last time, Admiral!
I've been waiting for you Obi-wan. We meet again at last. The circle is now complete. When I left you, I was but the learner, now I am the master.
The force is strong with you, young Skywalker, but you are not a Jedi yet.
And now your highness we will discuss the location of your hidden rebel base.
Asteroids do not concern me, Admiral! I want that ship, not excuses!
There will be a substantial reward for the one who finds the Millennium Falcon. You are free to use any methods necessary, but I want them alive. No disintegrations.
We would be honored if you would join us.
The Empire will compensate you, if he dies. Put him in.
Be careful not to choke on your aspirations, Director.

image.quote: Luke, you can destroy the Emperor. He has foreseen this. It is your destiny. Join me, and together we can rule the galaxy as father and son.
You are beaten. It is useless to resist. Don't let yourself be destroyed as Obi-Wan did.
